{"tid":1202113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［勁fight哥］成日話群龍無首，明明最好既領袖就喺面前","createTime":"2019-06-11T08:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T10:14:17.000Z","uid":166886,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"279647873ec8f6a31c9018fcbce039f74f5c5b36","tid":1202113,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:00:14.000Z","msg":"論才華演技-應屆最佳男配角<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uQOmvHY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuQOmvHY.png&h=9f30c089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n論樣貌-我喎？唔洗多講啦 髮線後移只係增加咗佢既成熟魅力同威嚴<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n83qcV1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn83qcV1.png&h=1cfbe586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n論領導力，有邊個憑一己之力可以喺舊燈或者呢度拿到個萬個正/負皮先，又有邊個有能力帶咁多人衝先<br />\n論個人能力，畢業於武術名校明愛馬登，一身橫練肌肉，加上大家都睇過唔少佢既英文演講，走出來領導一定冇人唔服！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jHixVJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jHixVJ.png&h=c57d103a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寧願要大家愛戴都唔要一百萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/PMVj1MX.png[/img］\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMVj1MX.png%5B%2Fimg%EF%BC%BD&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=9c06c56b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/PMVj1MX.png[/img］</a><br />\n<br />\n又團結到香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2X4taFR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2X4taFR.png&h=ec6815b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFGfz7x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFGfz7x.png&h=c4696fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctuMGNy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctuMGNy.png&h=daceecdd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9EQo0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9EQo0U.png&h=bbf695d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLPAz7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLPAz7B.png&h=0d3a5086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，唔該大家唔好亂咁篤，因為<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGqoJ1p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGqoJ1p.png&h=4b79e2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiAW31r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiAW31r.png&h=fc3e1851&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40066ad2a2e55af82c1df7cf80e6e2825454b9ad","tid":1202113,"uid":166886,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"補圖：寧願要市民愛戴都唔要錢<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asR7rgY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasR7rgY.png&h=6f0909fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34683c5a600d4bab47caa12d7981376dd606a16e","tid":1202113,"uid":166886,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:03:10.000Z","msg":"如果大家去野餐既時候見到勁fight哥<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈</span>唔好亂咁叫佢"},{"pid":"a77c79ea62ecef68939c66c31b663cfd5a150535","tid":1202113,"uid":134012,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"仲要做過飛虎<br />\n識好多戰術部署"},{"pid":"861f72379789a727b00b256189858460c388a921","tid":1202113,"uid":166886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"如果勁fight哥拿証據出來話冇去過，當日喺第二度既話請大家合作，<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈</span>唔好亂咁話佢有去"},{"pid":"e13588ad24d2a8aba31783270d91a2655198f100","tid":1202113,"uid":72253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db12e8ba3d478bc20d382055c938efd113ad9b63","tid":1202113,"uid":166886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T08:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"490acb85b0f2c20e88b5cda761ffe03636060f67","tid":1202113,"uid":144174,"like":19,"dis